HubSpot appears to have updated the gallery module, we had a script that enabled the progressive lazyload feature of the slider but it started causing issues ```$(".hs_cos_gallery &gt; div").each(function(){
    var opts = $(this).get(0).slick.options;
    opts.lazyLoad='progressive';
    $(this).slick('unslick').slick(opts);
  });```

If you have an array that has to be strings for whatever reason, I think you could use `|map` to turn them into proper numbers:
```{% set numbers = ["9", "8", "10"] %}
{% set sorted = numbers|map('int')|sort %}```
